{"tid":373272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[澳門人入] 水資源與海水化淡","createTime":"2017-08-25T02:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T06:59:17.000Z","uid":54481,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c279c0f21e113d01361aee06e608aa5ba6faae32","tid":373272,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T02:21:37.000Z","msg":"1.)2014至2016年，澳門水價每立方米約2.29元人民幣（約2.66港元）<br />\n2.)2015年供港東江水每平方米實際價格5.51元<br />\n3.)2015年以色列(李生)的海水化淡成本從10年前的每立方米三美元（約24港元），降到50美分（約3.8港元）。<br />\n4.)新加坡海水化淡每立方米約3.85港元<br />\n5.)與新加坡接壤的馬來西亞柔佛州（Johor），於本月較早前更要反過來，向新加坡買入飲用水。(2016年)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">澳門人，做人做鬼，自己諗<br />\nen唔enjoy依幾日60年代既生活?</span></span>"},{"pid":"da8b04f33e9f7893f3e9533d0b0973a8732d2a1f","tid":373272,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1401629a1f0cc6a3604421faf45ef8cef6168725","tid":373272,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f03ce247d41b5cc40325c97b8a7f22a5aacb10","tid":373272,"uid":49916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae8f7f66a8fcb6109999045cae7c622e6dce763","tid":373272,"uid":106544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"人地鍾意懷舊你理得人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89558f50671316f67663d9d1aefce48ceb67c567","tid":373272,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T23:13:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地鍾意懷舊你理得人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n猶太人人來了"},{"pid":"82775aee40538c9b25668a1630ef1c3b81f5e0e3","t